primary_asset_contracts.name: AToken Wallet
primary_asset_contracts.description:
AToken is a mobile wallet that supports secure and easy multi-asset storage.
Features of AToken Wallet
It has some stunning features below:
- Multi-asset Wallet
Support to store most tokens of 19 blockchains including BTC, ETH, ETC, EOS, ATOM, DOT and others. In the future, AToken will support more cryptos than ever to diversify the choice for users.

primary_asset_contracts.description: Ethereum Name Service (ENS) domains are secure domain names for the decentralized world. ENS domains provide a way for users to map human readable names to blockchain and non-blockchain resources, like Ethereum addresses, IPFS hashes, or website URLs. ENS domains can be bought and sold on secondary markets.
